Output docs/ai-demo.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 620
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Type "npx tsx src/index.tsx"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "s"
Sleep 7s
Escape
Sleep 500ms

Type "a"
Sleep 3s
Type "What's the main point of the article?"
Enter
Sleep 8s
Escape
Sleep 500ms

Ctrl+C
